際權力遠大於呢條條例所講嘅</span><br />\n基本上一個法庭可以做嘅佢都做到"},{"pid":"d67c107e0b2d84e150761787e2c82399c16b86cf","tid":1292021,"uid":212626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-07T06:59:20.000Z","msg":"有一樣嘢可能好多人會擔心<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">特首可唔可以干預？</span></span><br />\n佢想嘅話點解唔得<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">但係</span></span><br />\n由於呢個委員會係屬於<span style=\"color: red;\">司法程序</span><br />\n特首係行政機構嘅首長 如果插手就等同干擾司法獨立<br />\n視乎佢干擾嘅手法同程度 可能仲會有其他罪行<br />\n所以呢個情況唔太可能出現<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a233e357cac9903bffeaa100e4f7bacbad118d08","tid":1292021,"uid":173849,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-07T07:01:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"24f434c90a6783742d138f16c869d8489c809157","tid":1292021,"uid":206021,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-07T07:02:21.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"968c2b644559fbd45f8471914109da5f9127523c","tid":1292021,"uid":212626,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-07T07:06:07.000Z","msg":"警拒獨立調查原因：南丫海難官員入獄<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1263415/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1263415/page/1</a><br />\n呢個係另一單案例<br />\n最後<span style=\"color: red;\">海事處助理處長</span>蘇平治因公職人員行為失當罪被<span style=\"color: red;\">判處監禁16個月</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n亦有海事處人員比人發現講大話<span style=\"color: red;\">判處監禁</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://zh.wikipedia.org/wiki/南丫島撞船事故\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fzh.wikipedia.org%2Fwiki%2F%E5%8D%97%E4%B8%AB%E5%B3%B6%E6%92%9E%E8%88%B9%E4%BA%8B%E6%95%85&d=ycfrXf17TK8Hvu747cBakbHKdwoo7KeUephkEgg9e70%3D&h=fcfaef3e\" target=\"_blank\">https://zh.wikipedia.org/wiki/南丫島撞船事故</a>"},{"pid":"a